om-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>开发商 Channel 3 Entertainment 和发行商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/paradox-interactive">Paradox Interactive</a>推出了<em>Foundry</em> ，这是一款新的模拟游戏，它将<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/factorio"><em>Factorio</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/satisfactory"><em>Satisfactory</em></a>混合在一起，带来无限的协作体验。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/why-steam-next-fests-demos-are-a-vital-celebration-of-gamings-future-3459650#:~:text=Since%20it%20adopted%20the%20name,ahead%20of%20their%20game's%20launch.">为什么 Steam Next Fest 的演示是对游戏未来的重要庆祝</a></strong></li></ul><p>作为一款第一人称工厂建造沙盒模拟游戏，《Foundry》将把玩家置于一个无限程序生成的星球上，将其改造成科幻工业的堡垒。查看下面的公告预告片： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="FOUNDRY — 工厂建筑沙箱 |公告预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Gn6wfLTn8dM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>地形也不会阻止玩家在<em>铸造厂</em>实现他们的梦想——每个方块都可以被摧毁，新的方块可以放置在他们喜欢的任何地方。丛林和山脉等生物群落已经公布，后者允许在地表和地下的岩石中建造工厂。</p><p>一开始，从周围环境中开采资源，这些资源成为工厂的基础，而工厂又成为生产线、传送带和管道。进一步的研究可以提高技术的效率，最大限度地提高玩家工厂的生产力。</p><p> Channel 3 Entertainment 副总裁 Patrik Meder 在一份新闻稿中表示：“我们从 Itch.io 的<em>Foundry</em> Alpha 那里收到的压倒性积极反馈令人鼓舞，并凸显了这款游戏的巨大潜力。”</p><p> “为了充分发挥这一潜力，与完美的合作伙伴合作至关重要。由 Paradox Interactive 出版使我们能够实现<em>Foundry</em>的愿景和抱负。” </p><figure id="attachment_3508303" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3508303" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3508303" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/foundry-from-channel-3-entertainment-and-paradox-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3508303" class="wp-caption-text"> “铸造厂”信用：Paradox Interactive</figcaption></figure><p>好奇的模拟粉丝将能够在 Steam Next Fest 中了解该游戏提供的内容。演示版将于 10 月 9 日至 16 日期间通过 Steam 提供，但尚不清楚总共需要多长时间。</p><p>此外， <em>Foundry</em>将支持在线和离线多人游戏，且对玩家数量没有限制，但开发者再次没有透露这是否会成为演示版的一个功能。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，据报道，总部位于韦克菲尔德的开发商和发行商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/team17">Team17</a>据称将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/team17-to-reportedly-make-tens-of-redundancies-this-month-3507780">解雇其营销和质量保证部门的“数十名”员工</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/paradox-announces-free-demo-for-factorio-style-sim-foundry-3508228">Paradox 宣布“Factorio”风格的模拟游戏“Foundry”的免费演示版</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
