年 10 月 2 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>据报道，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dr-dre">Dr. Dre</a>合作制作的“Jesus Is King 2”曲目主要由第一张专辑中的歌曲混音而成，同时还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">Eminem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/pusha-t">Pusha T</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/2-chainz">2 Chainz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anderson-paak">Anderson</a>等客串。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anderson-paak">.Paak</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/asap-ferg">A$AP Ferg</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marsha-ambrosius">Marsha Ambrosius</a> （根据<a href="https://hiphopdx.com/news/kanye-west-dr-dre-jesus-is-king-2-leak#:~:text=Kanye%20West%20and%20Dr.%20Dre,on%20Monday%20(September%2025)." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>HipHopDX</em></a> ）。</p><p>新曲目包括 Dr. Dre 和 Snoop Dogg 合作的《This Is The Glory》、Pusha T 合作的《Blood of the Lamb》、A$AP Ferg 合作的《LA Monster》以及 Dre 和 2 Chainz 合作的《Our King》。还有一些来自西方的新诗句。</p><p>韦斯特（现在的名字是 Ye）早在 2019 年就首次宣布了《第二部分》， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-dr-dre-join-forces-jesus-king-part-ii-project-2575457">并表示它将“即将推出”</a> 。</p><p>目前尚不清楚叶目前是否因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-makes-twitter-comeback-after-meta-restricts-instagram-account-3325177">他去年发表的一系列有争议的言论而没有被贴上标签，这些言论被批评为反犹太主义</a>，或者他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-responds-to-white-lives-matter-backlash-everyone-knows-that-black-lives-matter-was-a-scam-3322278">“白人的命也是命”的噱头</a>引起了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-white-lives-matter-shirt-yeezy-show-paris-fashion-week-jaden-smith-boosie-respond-3321782">强烈的反对</a>。早在 2022 年 10 月，就有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-is-reportedly-no-longer-signed-to-def-jam-3335238">West 不再与唱片公司 Def Jam 签约</a>。</p><p>本月早些时候，韦斯特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-sues-over-music-leaks-on-instagram-3495367">起诉一名不知名的 Instagram 用户</a>，指控其将自己的音乐泄露到该社交媒体平台上。</p><p>在其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">卡迪·B</a>在一段视频中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-responds-to-kanye-west-clip-calling-her-an-illuminati-plant-3507799">回应了韦斯特称她为“光明会植物”的言论</a>，据报道该视频是从一部未发行的 2018 年纪录片中泄露的。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-reportedly-debuts-new-album-at-private-listening-party-in-italy-3508319">据报道，坎耶·韦斯特 (Kanye West) 在意大利私人试听派对上首次亮相的新专辑的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《国家报》的马特·伯宁格 (Matt Berninger) 和弟弟汤姆 (Tom) 正在制作情景喜剧《Dos Apes》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-nationals-matt-berninger-and-brother-tom-are-working-on-a-sitcom-dos-apes-3508341?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=国民队马特·伯宁格和汤姆兄弟正在制作情景喜剧《多斯猿》Andrew Trendell Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:40:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3508341 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="汤姆·伯宁格 (Tom Berninger) 和马特·伯宁格 (Matt Berninger) 于 2014 年在纽约。 （丹尼尔·祖赫尼克/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伯宁格告诉我们，这个“非常不同”的节目是如何基于一个虚构的独立乐队并以随身听成员为主角的</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-nationals-matt-berninger-and-brother-tom-are-working-on-a-sitcom-dos-apes-3508341">《国家报》的马特·伯宁格 (Matt Berninger) 和弟弟汤姆 (Tom) 正在制作情景喜剧《Dos Apes》，该消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="汤姆·伯宁格 (Tom Berninger) 和马特·伯宁格 (Matt Berninger) 于 2014 年在纽约。 （丹尼尔·祖赫尼克/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/national_matt_tom_berninger_sitcom_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">国家乐队</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matt-berninger">马特·伯宁格</a>向<em>《NME》</em>透露了他与兄弟汤姆合作的情景喜剧《 <em>Dos Apes》</em>的细节。</p><ul><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/the-national-matt-berninger-interview-new-albums-taylor-swift-3506365"><strong>阅读更多：</strong> 《国家报》的马特·伯宁格（Matt Berninger）：“意识到我是多么脆弱，这让我警醒”</a></li></ul><p>这个酝酿已久的项目于 2020 年首次被提及，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-nationals-matt-berninger-is-working-on-a-mistaken-for-strangers-movie-sequel-and-a-tv-show-2666871">马特·伯宁格 (Matt Berninger) 告诉<em>NME</em> ，他正在制作一部广受好评的电影<em>《误以为陌生人》</em>的续集</a>以及一部电视节目。 <em>《误以为陌生人》</em>于 2013 年发行，跟随伯宁格的兄弟汤姆加入乐队，并试图记录他们的旅程，但他作为巡演经理的角色也失败了。汤姆还执导了这部电影。</p><p>现在，在本周<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/the-national-matt-berninger-interview-new-albums-taylor-swift-3506365"><em>NME</em>的 In Conversation 采访</a>中，马特透露，该项目已经恢复并再次运行，在封锁期间作家受阻和抑郁症期间将其搁置 - 该节目基于摇滚乐队的原创材料并以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-walkmen">随身听</a>成员为特色。</p><p> “就像弗兰肯斯坦一样，一道闪电再次启动了它的心脏！”他说。 “这真是一场很棒的演出。它被称为<em>“Dos Apes”</em> ，随着流感大流行，我们不得不把它放下。<em>多斯猿</em>还活着，这就是我能说的。由于作家罢工之类的事情，没有发生任何事情，但我们拭目以待。</p><p> “我不会像以前那样淹没在项目中，但这是我真正想做的项目之一，而且它可能会发生。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《国民报》的马特·伯宁格 (Matt Berninger) 谈论对抗抑郁症、与泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的合作以及下一步的发展" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HLnrHEKs1Y0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>当被问及该剧的情节时，伯宁格回答道：“有很多来自自传的细节，但不仅仅是我的—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-walkmen">《随身听》</a>中的沃尔特·马丁和马特·巴里克也有各种各样的故事。我的兄弟汤姆本质上是一切的英雄。汤姆和我扮演我们自己，我的妻子不在其中，但这部剧的整个化学反应和 DNA 与我认为存在的任何东西都非常不同。</p><p> “这真的很酷、快乐又有趣。汤姆、卡琳（贝瑟、妻子兼合作者）和我制作的<em>《误以为陌生人</em>》纪录片抓住了这部电视节目的精神，但它不会是一部假纪录片或类似的东西。但谁知道呢？可能什么都不是。它可能永远存在于我们的笔记本电脑上。”</p><p> Speaking to <em>NME</em> about the episodic TV project back in 2020, Berninger said that he&#39;d been working on since around 2014.</p><p> “It&#39;s going great. There are a couple of versions of the TV show that we took around and pitched and developed,” he said at the time. “One we backed away from a long time ago because it was HBO and it was starting to become an indie rock <em>Girls</em> . Tom and I had to figure out what the heart and tone of <em>Mistaken For Strangers</em> was and we didn&#39;t want to make a half hour TV comedy on that level that HBO does.</p><p> “At one point about a year ago we were pitching a version of it to Netflix. In the lobby, there must have been about 17 or 18 people there to pitch. It was like all of people there with celebrities, all trying out for a part. There were so many people there that almost have a show. We&#39;re not that close, but almost everyone else I know is.” </p><figure id="attachment_3506367" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3506367" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3506367" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/national_interview_Graham_MacIndoe_landscape.jpg" alt="The National, 2023. Credit: Graham Macindoe" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/national_interview_Graham_MacIndoe_landscape.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/national_interview_Graham_MacIndoe_landscape-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/national_interview_Graham_MacIndoe_landscape-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/national_interview_Graham_MacIndoe_landscape-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/national_interview_Graham_MacIndoe_landscape-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/national_interview_Graham_MacIndoe_landscape-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3506367" class="wp-caption-text"> The National, 2023. Credit: Graham Macindoe</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/the-national-matt-berninger-interview-new-albums-taylor-swift-3506365">Read and watch our full interview with Berninger here</a> , where he also discusses “lighting the flame” after battling depression, what went into The National&#39;s two new albums &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-national-first-two-pages-of-frankenstein-review-3434616">First Two Pages Of Frankenstein</a> &#39; and &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-national-laugh-track-review-tracklist-lyrics-3498683">Laugh Track</a> &#39;, and the “joy” of working with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tAYLOR-SWIFT">Taylor Swift</a> .</p><p> Last week saw <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-national-london-alexandra-palace-review-photos-setlist-3505772">the band play two consecutive nights at London&#39;s Alexandra Palace</a> , while not repeating any songs in the setlists.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-nationals-matt-berninger-and-brother-tom-are-working-on-a-sitcom-dos-apes-3508341">The National&#39;s Matt Berninger and brother Tom are working on a sitcom, &#39;Dos Apes&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</